rComments: she was a great teacher and was passionate about what she was doing. It made the class very enjoyable.

She's a passionate professor, good lecturer.  Not much hmwk other than weekly readings (1 or 2 chapters).  2 books ,2 papers, and 2 exams.  Papers are graded easy.  The problem with the course are the exams, they're tough bc u have to memorize a ton of vocab from the textbook.  The 2 books are good and short.  Overall, semi-hard but a good class.
